introduction this proceeding concerns a determination made by the respondent, the commissioner of taxation ( the commissioner ), under part iva of the income tax assessment act 1936 (cth) ( the 1936 act ), that an amount should be included in the assessable income of the applicant, british american tobacco australia services limited (formerly known as wd &amp; ho wills (australia) limited) ( the taxpayer ).
